---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Campus Tech"
  description="Campus Tech is an independent tech review site built for college students. We test products honestly and only recommend what's actually worth your money."
>
  <div class="container about-wrap">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About Campus Tech</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          Campus Tech is an independent tech review site for college students. We started it because
          most tech review sites are written for people with unlimited budgets who upgrade their gear
          every year. That's not how students work.
        </p>
        <p>
          We focus on the things that actually matter for student life: battery life (will it last
          through your full class day?), weight (is it killing your back?), value (is it worth the
          money when you're on a student budget?), and longevity (will it hold up for 4+ years?).
        </p>

        <h2>How We Test</h2>
        <p>
          Every product we review, we buy ourselves. We use it as our daily driver for at least one
          week before writing anything. We test battery life at realistic screen brightness levels,
          not the "minimum brightness, Wi-Fi off" conditions manufacturers use.
        </p>
        <p>
          We're not in the business of giving everything 4+ stars. If something isn't worth buying,
          we say so.
        </p>

        <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          Some links on Campus Tech are affiliate links. If you click them and make a purchase, we
          earn a small commission — at no extra cost to you. This is how we keep the site free.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our affiliate relationships never influence our editorial opinions. We've given poor reviews
          to products we have affiliate links for, and we've enthusiastically recommended products
          we have no financial relationship with. Our only obligation is to you, the reader.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions, corrections, or product suggestions? <a href="/contact">Reach out here.</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="about-aside">
        <div class="about-values card">
          <h3>Our Values</h3>
          <ul class="values-list">
            <li>
              <span class="value-icon">🔬</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Hands-on testing only</strong>
                <p>We don't review products we haven't used.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="value-icon">💬</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Honest opinions</strong>
                <p>We'll tell you when to skip something, even if we have a link to it.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="value-icon">🎓</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Student-first perspective</strong>
                <p>Budget, portability, and durability matter more than specs.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="value-icon">🚫</span>
              <div>
                <strong>No paid reviews</strong>
                <p>We never accept payment for positive coverage.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-wrap { padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-values { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .about-values h3 { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .values-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .values-list li { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start; }
  .value-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .values-list strong { display: block; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
  .values-list p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
